Package: microscopR
Title: Data processing suite for micrographs
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: person("Peter", "Linders", email = "peter.linders@radboudumc.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package allows for the efficient importing of (confocal)
    micrographs acquired on various microscopes. Following this, this package
    supplies several functions (currently colocalization and ratiometric analysis)
    to further process images.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.1)
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
